Taking the following CSV file containing one article per row:
<id>,<creationDate>,<title>,<content> read all articles from the file inserted as an input to the program.

Once the file was successfully read, the following operations should be allowed to be performed:

orderAscByCreationDate
orderDescByCreationDate
orderAlphabeticallyByTitle

Each action can be invoked by pressing the corresponding number: 1, 2 or 3.
A nice human readable message must be printed next to each number.

The code must be sitting in the following package: com.javalearningproject.exercise1